Welcome to the dating panopticon.What happens when every misstep has the potential to go viral? In this episode, tech journalist @tanyenorth and sex and culture writer @magdajtaylor break down the dating panopticon — a world where love, gossip, and surveillance collide.From ghosting etiquette to the hacked Tea App, we explore how online whisper networks meant to protect women have turned into digital minefields, and what it takes to opt out of turning our romantic lives into content. And, we rehash the ancient, cautionary tale of the one and only West Elm Caleb.Listen now in the link in bio, or wherever you get your podcasts!#closealltabs #closealltabspodcast #surveillance #storytime #datingstories #tea<p><img src="https://prank-arum.github.io/Feeds/Instagram/magdajtaylor/6752117053294948202120.jpg"><p><a href="https://picnob.com/post/6752117053294948202120">Original post on Picnob</a>]]>
